          "effect": "You extend the staff with the force of a meteor, dealing 10d10 bludgeoning damage to a single creature within 120 feet and making it enfeebled 1 for 1 day. All other creatures within 10 feet of the target (except the staff\u2019s wielder) take 8d10 sonic damage (DC 43 basic Reflex save).",
