    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Also known as *Ruyi Bang*, this +3 major striking greater extending grievous bo staff is a legendary artifact wielded by the Monkey King, Sun Wukong. Unlike normal bo staves, the Staff of Sun Wukong is made of solid iron with two brilliant gold bands at either end.",
